    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six power unit. This high-revving mill utilizes individual throttle bodies and double VANOS variable valve timing to deliver linear power delivery up to an 8,000 RPM redline. Mated to a precise 6-speed manual transmission, the drivetrain utilizes a factory GKN limited-slip differential for optimal power transfer. The chassis remains taut, benefitting from documented subframe reinforcement and a recent refresh of the RTABs and FCABs. This example represents a balanced mechanical state, ideal for the purist seeking an authentic analog driving experience. Maintenance is current, including recent valve lash adjustments and rod bearing prophylaxis.",
