    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super reliable for all my daily errands and weekend trips. If you're looking for a dependable car that still looks great on the road, this is the one for you! I've taken good care of it, and I'd love to see it go to a great new home. Come take it for a spin!",
      "price": 28900.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
