      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 31
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available for acquisition is a mechanically sound E92 M3 featuring the high-revving S65 4.0L V8, renowned for its individual throttle bodies and 8,400 RPM redline. This unit is equipped with a tactile 6-speed manual gearbox and the M Variable Differential Lock for superior lateral traction. To address platform-specific longevity, the rod bearings have been replaced with treated shells and the throttle actuators have been upgraded. The chassis features Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and the factory carbon fiber roof panel for reduced polar moment of inertia. Maintenance records confirm consistent fluid intervals for the 10W-60 lubrication system, ensuring this naturally aspirated powerplant remains in peak operating condition.",
